title: found in teen fashion magazines and iphone app
author: I.M.C

comments.content:
The monogram looks like it uses Monogram KK by koeiekat:

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20140309064839im_/http:/typophile.com/files/MonogramKK_4393.jpg)
  
The monogram squeezes the letters together.  
 [http://www.dafont.com/monogram-kk.font](http://web.archive.org/web/20140309064839/http:/www.dafont.com/monogram-kk.font "http://www.dafont.com/monogram-kk.font")  
Koeiekat's font information is that it is a curly monogram letter based on Victorian Initials.  
There may be other fonts based on the same old initials.  
Don
